---

<PageLayout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
>
  
  <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-4">
    <Breadcrumbs 
      items={[
        { name: "Home", url: "/" },
        { name: "Service Areas", url: "/service-areas" },
        { name: "Burlington" }
      ]}
    />
  </div>

<!-- Location Hero -->
  <Hero 
    title="Waterproofing Burlington"
    subtitle="Professional basement waterproofing and foundation repair serving all Burlington neighborhoods. 25-year warranty, free inspection."
    primaryCTA={{ text: "Get Free Burlington Quote", href: "/free-inspection" }}
    secondaryCTA={{ text: "Call: 437-545-0067", href: "tel:437-545-0067" }}
    backgroundImage="/images/dryspace_hero_desktop.webp"
    badge="Serving Burlington"
  />

  <!-- Internal Links -->
  <section class="py-8 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <InternalLinks category="location" currentPage="burlington" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <Stats />

  <!-- Local Information Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">WATERPROOFING SERVICES IN BURLINGTON</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg  max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Burlington's location between Lake Ontario and the Niagara Escarpment creates extraordinary waterproofing challenges. From lakefront properties dealing with fluctuating water tables to escarpment homes managing steep slope drainage, our team understands the complex geology of glacial deposits transitioning from sandy lakeshore to limestone bedrock. With 186,000 residents and homes averaging 35-45 years old, foundation protection requires specialized expertise.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 p-6 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Burlington's Unique Geography</h3>
            <p class="text-cyan-700 text-sm">
              The dramatic elevation change from Lake Ontario (75m) to the Niagara Escarpment (250m) creates complex water flow patterns. 
              Escarpment springs, seasonal runoff, and lake-effect precipitation combine with varying soil conditions to challenge traditional waterproofing approaches.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200  p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">BURLINGTON QUICK FACTS</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600 ">
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Population</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">186,000</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Average Home Age</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">35-45 YEARS</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Annual Rainfall</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">805MM ANNUALLY</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Frost Line</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">1.0 METERS</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Flood Risk</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">MODERATE</span>
              </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-navy-900 border-2 border-slate-200  p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">BURLINGTON'S WATERPROOFING CHALLENGES</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300">
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Niagara Escarpment limestone creates natural water channels</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Lake Ontario influence creates fluctuating groundwater</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Glacial soil deposits shift with seasonal moisture</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Steep slopes concentrate spring runoff</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Lake-effect snow creates heavy spring melts</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Mature trees near foundations create root infiltration</span>
              </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Burlington Neighborhoods & Their Unique Challenges</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Each Burlington neighborhood faces distinct waterproofing challenges based on elevation, soil type, and proximity to water features:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">ALDERSHOT (Lakefront)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Sandy soils, fluctuating water table, Lake Ontario influence</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">BRANT HILLS (Mid-Escarpment)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Clay deposits, spring water seepage, slope drainage issues</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">TYANDAGA (Upper Escarpment)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Limestone bedrock, natural springs, steep slope runoff</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 border border-slate-100 rounded">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">MILLCROFT (Creek Valley)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Sixteen Mile Creek proximity, seasonal flooding risk</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {["Aldershot","Roseland","Brant Hills","Tyandaga","Millcroft","Palmer","Orchard","Headon Forest"].map((neighborhood) => (
              <span class="border-2 border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 text-sm">
                {neighborhood}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <Services />

  <!-- Location Features -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">WHY CHOOSE DRYSPACE IN BURLINGTON</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Local expertise combined with industry-leading warranties and service
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Highlighted Features -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        {locationFeatures.filter(f => f.highlight).map((feature) => (
          <div class="bg-amber-500 border-2 border-slate-700 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">{feature.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-900">{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <!-- Regular Features -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {locationFeatures.filter(f => !f.highlight).map((feature) => (
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 p-6 hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">{feature.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <Process />


  <!-- Location Image Showcase -->
  <LocationImageShowcase city="Burlington" />

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <Testimonials />

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">BURLINGTON WATERPROOFING FAQS</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Common questions from Burlington homeowners</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {locationFAQs.map((faq, index) => (
          <details class="mb-4 border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase pr-4">{faq.question}</h3>
                <span class="text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0 text-2xl">+</span>
              </div>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-0">
              <p class="text-slate-600">{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">PROTECT YOUR BURLINGTON PROPERTY</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Whether your home sits along Lake Ontario's shore or high on the Niagara Escarpment, we have the specialized expertise to protect your investment from Burlington's unique water challenges.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/free-inspection"
            class="bg-amber-500 text-black px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors uppercase"
          >
            Get Escarpment-Specialized Assessment
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/contact"
            class="border-2 border-white text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors uppercase"
          >
            Request Quote
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center text-cyan-400">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase">24/7 Emergency Service Available</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(localBusinessSchema)}>
<BreadcrumbSchema items={[{name: 'Home', url: '/'}, {name: 'Locations', url: '/locations'}, {name: 'Burlington'}]} />
